  "texts": [
    "Early stopping on validation loss was used, with patience of five epochs and tolerance of 10 -5.",
    "The experiments suggested 45 epochs to be optimal; the pre-trained model was fine-tuned on the whole dataset accordingly.",
    "The models of the last five fine-tuning epochs were used to design molecules.",
    "A total of 10,240 designs for temperature values ranging from 1.0 to 2.0 (step size 0.25) were generated per temperature and model, totaling 5 × 5 × 10, 240 = 256K designs.",
    "The novel and unique molecules among those designs were ranked by their fine-tuning loglikelihood (Eq."
  ]
